== 家庭 ==
母亲彭平是[[彭湃|彭湃]]侄女。<ref>{{Cite web|title=专访｜未来科学大奖得主彭实戈：数学是一旦对了，到处都对|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9136817|access-date=2021-06-29|author=虞涵棋|date=2020-09-12|work=|publisher=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629183147/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9136817|dead-url=no}}</ref>外祖父[[彭汉垣|彭汉垣]]是革命烈士，生父黄显群亦是革命烈士。<ref>{{Cite web|title=数学家彭实戈：中国金融数学的开创者|url=https://www.view.sdu.edu.cn/info/1011/38659.htm|access-date=2021-06-29|date=2008-10-10|work=|publisher=[[山东大学|山东大学]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629183827/https://www.view.sdu.edu.cn/info/1011/38659.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

